Before she reemerged
from that funk

00:25:15.340 --> 00:25:18.790 align:middle line:84%
and started her school strike
for global climate change,

00:25:18.790 --> 00:25:22.280 align:middle line:84%
she seems to be a
highly sensitive kid.

00:25:22.280 --> 00:25:23.080 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Clearly.

00:25:23.080 --> 00:25:23.530 align:middle line:90%
>>JAWER: Yes.

00:25:23.530 --> 00:25:24.460 align:middle line:90%
Now I don't know whether--

00:25:24.460 --> 00:25:25.240 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Passionately.

00:25:25.240 --> 00:25:26.282 align:middle line:90%
>>JAWER: Very passionate.

00:25:26.282 --> 00:25:27.908 align:middle line:84%
And she does have
an Asperger's--

00:25:27.908 --> 00:25:29.200 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: High function autism.

00:25:29.200 --> 00:25:30.620 align:middle line:90%
>>JAWER: High functional autism.

