00:25:32.920 --> 00:25:33.190 align:middle line:90%
years.

00:25:33.190 --> 00:25:35.920 align:middle line:84%
Her parents really did not know
what was going on with her.

00:25:35.920 --> 00:25:37.300 align:middle line:84%
But she went into
this depression

00:25:37.300 --> 00:25:38.810 align:middle line:90%
then she came out this crusader.

00:25:38.810 --> 00:25:39.610 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

