00:35:08.060 --> 00:35:09.823 align:middle line:90%
this one is just fascinating.

00:35:09.823 --> 00:35:11.240 align:middle line:84%
>>JAWER: This
didn't hurt anybody.

00:35:11.240 --> 00:35:12.412 align:middle line:90%
