00:36:04.770 --> 00:36:05.570 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:36:05.570 --> 00:36:07.508 align:middle line:84%
>>JAWER: And a large
percentage of them

00:36:07.508 --> 00:36:09.300 align:middle line:84%
