00:36:11.550 --> 00:36:14.660 align:middle line:84%
I was investigating poor indoor
air quality in sick buildings

00:36:14.660 --> 00:36:15.660 align:middle line:90%
and some of these folks.

00:36:15.660 --> 00:36:19.760 align:middle line:84%
So there seems to be some sort
of overlap between emotion,

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:23.600 align:middle line:84%
especially displaced,
dissociated feelings,

00:36:23.600 --> 00:36:25.940 align:middle line:84%
and the possibility
