00:36:29.510 --> 00:36:33.890 align:middle line:84%
may also borrow from
some form of electricity

00:36:33.890 --> 00:36:36.365 align:middle line:90%
to gain their momentum.

00:36:36.365 --> 00:36:37.490 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It's fascinating.

00:36:37.490 --> 00:36:39.540 align:middle line:84%
I can say just quickly
on a personal level--

00:36:39.540 --> 00:36:41.630 align:middle line:84%
and then we'll wrap it
up here, because there's

00:36:41.630 --> 00:36:44.780 align:middle line:84%
so many more of these that
people can read in your book.

00:36:44.780 --> 00:36:47.700 align:middle line:84%
But I have a particular
condition I was born with.

00:36:47.700 --> 00:36:52.400 align:middle line:84%
And I remember this one doctor
that I go to was looking at me

00:36:52.400 --> 00:36:55.390 align:middle line:84%
and said I've never seen such
an electrical system, such

00:36:55.390 --> 00:36:57.660 align:middle line:90%
an active electrical system.

00:36:57.660 --> 00:37:00.590 align:middle line:84%
So what happens when I go into
these things, these crises,

00:37:00.590 --> 00:37:02.540 align:middle line:84%
you might call them
before passing out

00:37:02.540 --> 00:37:05.990 align:middle line:84%
or whatnot is I feel that all
the electricity is flying away

00:37:05.990 --> 00:37:06.830 align:middle line:90%
from my body.

00:37:06.830 --> 00:37:08.870 align:middle line:84%
That's how I would
actually describe it.

00:37:08.870 --> 00:37:10.250 align:middle line:90%
All the electricity is going.

00:37:10.250 --> 00:37:11.750 align:middle line:84%
And if there's
someone who knows how

00:37:11.750 --> 00:37:13.670 align:middle line:84%
to work with
electricity nearby, they

00:37:13.670 --> 00:37:18.650 align:middle line:84%
can cap the areas it escapes
our body and for all people.

00:37:18.650 --> 00:37:22.010 align:middle line:84%
And one of them is right here
at the base of the neck to trap

00:37:22.010 --> 00:37:23.540 align:middle line:84%
that in there so
it can't leak out.

00:37:23.540 --> 00:37:26.150 align:middle line:84%
And then it flies out my
fingers and everything.

00:37:26.150 --> 00:37:29.660 align:middle line:84%
But what I noticed is if
you control the emotions

00:37:29.660 --> 00:37:31.940 align:middle line:84%
and don't become
afraid at that time,

00:37:31.940 --> 00:37:34.220 align:middle line:84%
if I can control
my emotions, I can

00:37:34.220 --> 00:37:37.850 align:middle line:84%
stop the flow of the
electricity out of my body

00:37:37.850 --> 00:37:39.920 align:middle line:84%
and maybe not even
go unconscious.

00:37:39.920 --> 00:37:44.720 align:middle line:84%
But if I go into any fear at
all, the electricity flies away

00:37:44.720 --> 00:37:45.580 align:middle line:90%
and I'm out.

00:37:45.580 --> 00:37:47.330 align:middle line:84%
>>JAWER: Yes, and
that's been demonstrated

00:37:47.330 --> 00:37:48.470 align:middle line:90%
with some of the cases.

00:37:48.470 --> 00:37:51.380 align:middle line:84%
There's a guy named Bill Roll
who's probably the most famous

00:37:51.380 --> 00:37:54.320 align:middle line:84%
of the poltergeist
investigators.

00:37:54.320 --> 00:37:59.090 align:middle line:84%
And it's typically
children-- it can be adults,

00:37:59.090 --> 00:38:02.120 align:middle line:84%
but it's typically adolescents
or preadolescents that seem

00:38:02.120 --> 00:38:04.712 align:middle line:84%
to be the focus of these
poltergeist cases--

00:38:04.712 --> 00:38:06.170 align:middle line:84%
when they get
therapy and when they

00:38:06.170 --> 00:38:09.820 align:middle line:84%
are allowed to talk
about their feelings,

00:38:09.820 --> 00:38:13.110 align:middle line:84%
the intensity of the
phenomena is reduced.

00:38:13.110 --> 00:38:13.910 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:38:13.910 --> 00:38:15.390 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, it is interesting.

00:38:15.390 --> 00:38:16.580 align:middle line:90%
It's an electrical universe.

00:38:16.580 --> 00:38:18.380 align:middle line:90%
We're electrical creatures.

00:38:18.380 --> 00:38:20.930 align:middle line:84%
We're working with thoughts
that have electrical components

00:38:20.930 --> 00:38:22.080 align:middle line:90%
to them as well.

00:38:22.080 --> 00:38:25.100 align:middle line:84%
And we're working with who
knows what just beyond the veil

00:38:25.100 --> 00:38:27.810 align:middle line:84%
and who knows what from
beyond time and space.

00:38:27.810 --> 00:38:29.840 align:middle line:90%
And so you're saying it sounds--

00:38:29.840 --> 00:38:31.760 align:middle line:84%
just to sum it up a
little bit before you

00:38:31.760 --> 00:38:34.220 align:middle line:84%
have your kind of final
thoughts on this--

00:38:34.220 --> 00:38:37.660 align:middle line:84%
that when we come into the
world in a more traumatic way

00:38:37.660 --> 00:38:40.510 align:middle line:84%
or suffer very early
trauma in our lives,

00:38:40.510 --> 00:38:44.710 align:middle line:84%
it creates a dissociation that
allows us to kind of almost

00:38:44.710 --> 00:38:47.710 align:middle line:84%
be open more to these
exceptional, what you

00:38:47.710 --> 00:38:51.010 align:middle line:84%
call exceptional situations,
or talents, or skills

00:38:51.010 --> 00:38:51.940 align:middle line:90%
in this life.

00:38:51.940 --> 00:38:54.310 align:middle line:84%
>>JAWER: Yes, it doesn't seem
to be a conscious choice.

00:38:54.310 --> 00:38:56.950 align:middle line:90%
That some people have it.

00:38:56.950 --> 00:38:59.080 align:middle line:90%
Other people can develop it.

00:38:59.080 --> 00:39:00.550 align:middle line:90%
But yes, that's essentially it.

00:39:00.550 --> 00:39:02.440 align:middle line:90%
And emotion being the key.

00:39:02.440 --> 00:39:06.740 align:middle line:84%
Again, I believe that feelings
have a profundity to them.

00:39:06.740 --> 00:39:07.540 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Oh, yeah.

00:39:07.540 --> 00:39:08.620 align:middle line:84%
They're giving us a
lot of information.

00:39:08.620 --> 00:39:09.460 align:middle line:90%
>>JAWER: They're physical.

00:39:09.460 --> 00:39:10.260 align:middle line:90%
They're mental.

00:39:10.260 --> 00:39:11.410 align:middle line:90%
They're spiritual.

00:39:11.410 --> 00:39:13.780 align:middle line:10%
And I think that
feelings combine

00:39:13.780 --> 00:39:15.100 align:middle line:10%
all of those aspects of us.

00:39:15.100 --> 00:39:16.690 align:middle line:10%
So we never want to
sell our feelings short.

00:39:16.690 --> 00:39:17.490 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Never.

00:39:17.490 --> 00:39:19.660 align:middle line:10%
Because they're
directly emanating also,

00:39:19.660 --> 00:39:22.120 align:middle line:10%
I believe, from the
subconscious and everything

00:39:22.120 --> 00:39:24.020 align:middle line:10%
that's ever been and
ever happened within us.

00:39:24.020 --> 00:39:26.260 align:middle line:84%
And if you have a feeling,
