00:39:27.850 --> 00:39:29.560 align:middle line:90%
There's information in there.

00:39:29.560 --> 00:39:31.840 align:middle line:84%
And so you're right, we
shouldn't-- we should never

00:39:31.840 --> 00:39:33.310 align:middle line:90%
ignore our feelings.

